 out on the seashore ♪</i>

00:39.637 --> 00:46.512
<i> ♪ Only I can hear the Sirens ♪</i>

00:46.545 --> 00:52.685
<i> ♪ Phantom voices
 calling me home ♪</i>

00:52.718 --> 00:58.058
<i> ♪ Like day dawning
 in my heart ♪</i>

01:08.400 --> 01:11.737
<i> SIREN (V.O.) My whole life,
 I've dreamt of water.</i>

01:11.769 --> 01:15.740
<i> Not just being in it,
 or swimming in it...</i>

01:15.774 --> 01:18.677
<i> but living in it.</i>

01:18.710 --> 01:24.816
<i> Breathing it, tasting it,
 loving it.</i>

01:24.849 --> 01:29.421
<i>And yet, in life, I stay pretty
far away from it.</i>

01:29.454 --> 01:30.856
